initialization
initialize
	"Set the lesson description"

	super initialize.
	
	self lessonName: 'Lesson 02 - Loops'.
	self lessonDescription: 'Here we are introducing loops in Squeak! Use only one instruction to move the mouse in one direction: Repeat the number of times that the mouse has to follow these orders and select the right direction. For example: "5 timesRepeat: [ mouse moveDown]."
Use as few code lines as possible. Good luck!'.